{"tid":449720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強姦親母】為錢起爭執 逆子姦63歲媽再拗斷佢條頸","createTime":"2017-10-27T12:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T13:28:56.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"349aaffb25b9695d06e0dac0bee78f7c097b7275","tid":449720,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171027/large/1509069903_d5cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171027%2Flarge%2F1509069903_d5cd.jpg&h=2188af78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國俄亥俄州一名逆子與63歲母親為錢起爭執後，竟強姦她再把她的頸弄斷。46歲逆子周三承認強姦、襲擊及綁架罪，被判囚11年。<br />\n<br />\n當局為保護受害人身份未有公佈逆子姓名，他在庭上曾聲稱：「我連發生甚麼事都不知道，我昏倒了，有人在我飲品中『加料』。我就連發生了甚麼事都不知道。」<br />\n案發在今年3月，逆子與母親在家中因金錢問題爭執，逆子先拳毆她，之後將她強姦。母親不理全身赤裸跑往鄰居求救，未料逆子趕至，將她捉住並拋過圍欄，令她跌入家中後園。逆子後來呼呼大睡，母親才報警求助，警員到場時他仍在睡。<br />\n母親頸部脊椎骨骨折、身體出現瘀傷割傷，另大腿內側及背部被咬傷。當局在逆子的性器官找到屬於他母親的DNA。"},{"pid":"ec460bc95415170280537b096f6610405fde7ee8","tid":449720,"uid":155509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1dcd30631773d1b595bf0f9837bb35add8c9f8f","tid":449720,"uid":111644,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae1cce170bfa7eae7dde4fe34ed7ca1ea37800f","tid":449720,"uid":51978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:20:17.000Z","msg":"又係nigga？"},{"pid":"d9eb0ea4ba807a440374cdf121e78b25db24760f","tid":449720,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets